{"tid":1411271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【對抗黑警記者會】我地星期一至五只做文宣, update連儂牆","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T04:20:45.000Z","uid":37528,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0b001c8d22de1ce1be53b873f8180cc07985e7","tid":1411271,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"政府同黑警日日開記者會想洗腦想分化，我地就星期一至五唔好做野，只做好文宣工作<br />\n唔好步雨革後塵<br />\n我地集中星期六，日先搞活動，好似尋日咁對準政權<br />\n<br />\n星期一至五我地可以做：<br />\n1. update連儂牆資訊<br />\n2. 流動廣播警黑合作<br />\n3. 宣傳星期六日既行動<br />\n4. 搞鄉黑，起底<br />\n5. 老豆搵仔<br />\n<br />\n我地要贏就要鬥智鬥力，唔好踩政府既陷阱<br />\n記著雨革既教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3012a7b9254a6840e165be7673cf6ef4a39d48d3","tid":1411271,"uid":37528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:20:37.000Z","msg":"大家要記得我地之前既文宣係好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5556271a2302045f9002c8b6eb5e6c643fadc84","tid":1411271,"uid":67118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:21:08.000Z","msg":"我認同！！"},{"pid":"a71486662a3720d38d4d10e22f262e0f187096c8","tid":1411271,"uid":44174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:21:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7854b4e7200e2c81c37a2bbc6e6b3ec0090f908f","tid":1411271,"uid":17154,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46e63b90a0b7102e79cd400a0a05faa09a84b5f7","tid":1411271,"uid":79181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:22:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命<br />\n破而後立 涅槃重生"},{"pid":"c7a97c00e36f4a5c9531c1abff793ba7491c7c0f","tid":1411271,"uid":78184,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:23:45.000Z","msg":"叫民主派幫手日日開返記者會，搵示威者、街坊同受害者譴責政府"},{"pid":"33d6e9aec6d7334eac676cae8047ddaf4f399dc4","tid":1411271,"uid":37528,"like":0